???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
?                                Release Notes                                ?
???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
 
               Only use the skins included with this release!
            Other or old skins may, or more likly will, not work.

???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????

  This includes only the stuff that&#039;s in CVS. No other shit like scripts are
  added. This is done to ensure that this release is as bugfree as possible.

               Skins Included are: Project Mayhem III and MC360.


???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
?                                 Change Log                                  ?
???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????

 - 28-09-2006 fixed: mockups with programs in root of bookmarks.

 - 27-09-2006 fixed: shoutcast listings broke after the url parsing fixes

 - 26-09-2006 fixed: Milkdrop - crash when changing preset packs when preset
 was locked

 - 26-09-2006 fixed: Milkdrop - started with default preset when preset
 was locked

 - 26-09-2006 fixed: first packet received by video decoder in dvdplayer
 after a flush would be from previouse set of data (more junk frames
 than needed)

 - 26-09-2006 fixed: progressbar didn&#039;t show on chapter change

 - 26-09-2006 fixed: skip buttons in osd always changed file not
 chapter in dvd&#039;s

 - 26-09-2006 changed: libdvdnav.dll and libdvdcss-2. dll updated with
 simpler cache and builtin layerchange error detection.

 - 26-09-2006 fixed: Ftp directory didn&#039;t handle failed listings
 very gratiously.

 - 25-09-2006 fixed: Initial partymode list was not randomized
 (always database order).

 - 25-09-2006 fixed: Initial image shown when viewing a
 picture/slideshow was sometimes blank.

 - 25-09-2006 changed: TTF rendering speed up.

 - 24-09-2006 fixed: memory leak when exiting credits

 - 24-09-2006 fixed: leaving the screensaver could cause black screens
 for non-dimmed screensaver modes

 - 24-09-2006 fixed: url parser choked on http urls containing ;, #,
 also for urls with ? but no filename after host

 - 24-09-2006 fixed: item 7 was not remembered in large item view

 - 24-09-2006 fixed: no sound when playing dvr-ms files
 (switched back to mplayer demuxer with fix for it&#039;s choppy playback )

 - 24-09-2006 updated: Hungarian language file (Thnx to bali001)

 - 24-09-2006 updated: Indonesian language file (Thnx to djoens)

 - 24-09-2006 updated: Spanish language file (Thnx to jose_t)

 - 24-09-2006 updated: Slovenian language file (Thnx to xsiluro)

???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
?                                Install Notes                                ?
???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????

             1. Make backup of any old files that you have edited.
          (Sources.xml & other files located in the UserData folder.)

               2. Rename the default.xbe to fit your bios config!

                       3. FTP all the files to your Xbox.

???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
?                                  Other Info                                 ?
???????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
